dId>.s-card.json`；画布节点与 conf 一致 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":110,"content":"| 画布删除 CallCard | 从 `conf.cards[]` 移除；**删除**对应 s-card 文件（若 entryCardId 指向该卡则阻止或强制改入口） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":111,"content":"| 保存整包 | `editorGraphToBundle` 写回 **conf.cards 与磁盘卡文件并集**（以画布为准），禁止只改 layout 不改 conf |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":112,"content":"| orphan 磁盘卡 | 未在 conf 索引的 s-card → validate `CARD_FILE_ORPHAN` warning；保存时可清理或保留策略写清 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":113,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":114,"content":"**禁止：** 仅会话内新增节点，保存后 conf 仍只有打开时的卡列表。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":115,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":116,"content":"### 2.3 entryCardId 与 effect.critical","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":117,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":118,"content":"| 项 | 口径 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":119,"content":"|----|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":120,"content":"| entryCardId | 包配置或章节浮窗可 Select 本包 cardId；新建包默认指向首张 story 卡或占位 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":121,"content":"| critical | 读盘保留；投影不丢；Effect 面板 boolean「失败则中止后续」；写回 effect.critical |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":122,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":123,"content":"### 2.4 ExitCondition 编辑器 v1（P0）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":124,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":125,"content":"**问题：** 现 `conditionSummary` 仅 UI 人话；写盘用 `base.condition ?? DEFAULT_CONDITION`，改 summary **不改**引擎 condition。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":162,"content":"","con