{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-cc2eaf8e-392e-4a03-b429-eb6d81edaef6-37\nfc_bbe625ad-8069-9748-a42a-bc46e95580c9_0","tool_call":{"grepToolCall":{"args":{"pattern":"free-cards|freeCards|schedule-cards|writeSchedule|ScheduleCard","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2","glob":"*.{ts,tsx}","caseInsensitive":false,"multiline":false,"toolCallId":"call-cc2eaf8e-392e-4a03-b429-eb6d81edaef6-37\nfc_bbe625ad-8069-9748-a42a-bc46e95580c9_0","offset":0},"result":{"success":{"pattern":"free-cards|freeCards|schedule-cards|writeSchedule|ScheduleCard","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2","outputMode":"content","workspaceResults":{"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine":{"content":{"matches":[],"totalLines":0,"totalMatchedLines":0,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-cc2eaf8e-392e-4a03-b429-eb6d81edaef6-37\nfc_bbe625ad-8069-9748-a42a-bc46e95580c9_0","startedAtMs":"1784770032161","completedAtMs":"1784770032320"},"model_call_id":"3bb1eaa0-dc1e-4666-b7a1-f546fede52a6-2-du1e","session_id":"13d95b2c-2da1-4bb3-a463-cffe162be1c5","timestamp_ms":1784770032270}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-cc2eaf8e-392e-4a03-b429-eb6d81edaef6-39\nfc_bbe625ad-8069-9748-a42a-bc46e95580c9_2","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","offset":184,"limit":90},"result":{"success":{"content":"## 3. Content 工作区磁盘布局\n\n创建故事包 = 在硬盘上新建目录 `data/storis-packages/<packageId>/`。  \n**大故事按文件拆开**：包配置一份、每张卡一个文件；禁止把全部卡内联进单一巨型 JSON 作为编辑真源。\n\n```text\ndata/\n  workspace.json\n  characters/\n    <agentId>.json\n  tools/\n    registry.json                 # 非真源／预留导出；ToolRegistry v1 = 代码 builtinRegistry（见需求 13）\n  assets/\n    meta/<assetId>.json           # 全局资产元数据真源（见需求 14）\n    files/...\n  storis-packages/                    # 故事包根目录正式名（拼写定稿；全仓改名另立项）\n    <packageId>/                      # 例：golden_handoff/\n      story.conf.json                 # 包级唯一配置（轻量；cards 只登记 cardId；可选 assetRefs）\n      canvas.layout.json              # 画布坐标/泳道旁车；引擎忽略\n      cards/\n        <cardId>.s-card.json          # 单卡真源；由 cardId 拼文件名载入\n  # 角色真源仅 characters/；包内禁止 agents[] 第二份定义\n  users/\n    index.json\n    <userId>/\n      profile.save.json           # 薄存档；不含万级 episodic\n  memory/\n    memory.sqlite                 # Memory 真源（见技术设计 20）\n  logs/\n    engine-YYYYMMDD.jsonl\n```\n\n### 3.1 `story.conf.json`（每包唯一）\n\n```json\n{\n  \"schemaVersion\": 1,\n  \"packageId\": \"golden_handoff\",\n  \"title\": \"黄金样例：转介\",\n  \"participants\": [\"doubao-sister\", \"xiaoyu\"],\n  \"entryCardId\": \"doubao_intro_outbound\",\n  \"cards\": [\n    { \"cardId\": \"doubao_intro_outbound\" },\n    { \"cardId\": \"xiaoyu_waiting_user\" }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n- `cards[]` **只含索引**（可选再加列表预览用 `title`），**不内嵌**卡 body。\n- 载入规则：`cardId` → `cards/<cardId>.s-card.json`。\n- conf 有 id 但文件缺失 → 校验 **error**；磁盘有多余 `.s-card.json` 未登记 → **warning**（可忽略或提示登记）。\n\n### 3.2 `*.s-card.json`（单卡）\n\n完整 `CallCardDefinition`（见需求 [01](../需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md)）。编辑/保存单卡只读写对应文件；运行时可按需 load，再写入 `CallSession.frozenCard`。\n\n逻辑上的「整包 StoryPackage」由 Host **组装视图**（conf + 已加载卡）；磁盘真源永远是分文件。\n\n### 3.3 Free 卡路径（与角色库）\n\n```text\ndata/characters/<agentId>.json\ndata/characters/free-cards/<freeCardId>.s-card.json\n```\n\n- Free 卡**不进** `storis-packages/`；由 `CharacterDef.freeCardId` 引用。\n- 纯 Free 通话 Session.`packageId = FREE_PACKAGE_ID`（`\"__free__\"`）；**禁止**创建或 load `storis-packages/__free__/`。\n- 详见 [11 §4](../需求/11-角色与社交.md)。\n\n`workspace.json` 示例字段：`schemaVersion`、`engineMinVersion`、`title`。\n\nStudio 主路径：\n\n| 路由 | 职责 |\n|------|------|\n| `/stories` | 故事列表；创建 = 新建 `storis-packages/<id>/` + 空 conf + 空 cards/ |\n| `/stories/[packageId]` | 画布；进门先 UserGate |\n| `/characters` | 全局角色库 |\n| `/debugger` | 先 UserGate，再调试台 |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Studio 用户门禁（无密码）\n\n- **无密码**；本地开发态选定 `userId` 即可。\n- 可复用组件 **`UserGate`**（非独立业务页）：列表 / 新增 / 选择 / 删除；可塞进 MUI `Dialog`。\n- **触发点**：\n  1. `/debugger` 进入时（必选）\n  2. `/stories` 点击某故事或「创建故事」时（保险门禁）\n- 故事**编辑逻辑**不依赖用户（改的是 Content）；门禁只为后续调试/预览/校验需要 Profile 时建立上下文。","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":510,"fileSize":20232,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","readRange":{"startLine":184,"endLine":273},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-cc2eaf8e-392e-4a03-b429-eb6d81edaef6-39\nfc_bbe625ad-8069-9748-a42a-bc46e95580c9_2","startedAtMs":"1784770032285","completedAtMs":"1784770032432"},"model_call_id":"3bb1eaa0-dc1e-4666-b7a1-f546fede52a6-2-du1e","session_id":"13d95b2c-2da1-4bb3-a463-cffe162be1c5","timestamp_ms":1784770032386}
