{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-8e4d1bff-01bb-4a8d-8809-bd3ce5a5bf74-65\nfc_e7810171-6a4b-9edb-9268-d9b7529019dd_3","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","offset":240,"limit":30},"result":{"success":{"content":"逻辑上的「整包 StoryPackage」由 Host **组装视图**（conf + 已加载卡）；磁盘真源永远是分文件。\n\n### 3.3 Free 卡路径（与角色库）\n\n```text\ndata/characters/<agentId>.json\ndata/characters/free-cards/<freeCardId>.s-card.json\n```\n\n- Free 卡**不进** `storis-packages/`；由 `CharacterDef.freeCardId` 引用。\n- 纯 Free 通话 Session.`packageId = FREE_PACKAGE_ID`（`\"__free__\"`）；**禁止**创建或 load `storis-packages/__free__/`。\n- 详见 [11 §4](../需求/11-角色与社交.md)。\n\n`workspace.json` 示例字段：`schemaVersion`、`engineMinVersion`、`title`。\n\nStudio 主路径：\n\n| 路由 | 职责 |\n|------|------|\n| `/stories` | 故事列表；创建 = 新建 `storis-packages/<id>/` + 空 conf + 空 cards/ |\n| `/stories/[packageId]` | 画布；进门先 UserGate |\n| `/characters` | 全局角色库 |\n| `/debugger` | 先 UserGate，再调试台 |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Studio 用户门禁（无密码）\n\n- **无密码**；本地开发态选定 `userId` 即可。\n- 可复用组件 **`UserGate`**（非独立业务页）：列表 / 新增 / 选择 / 删除；可塞进 MUI `Dialog`。","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":510,"fileSize":20232,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","readRange":{"startLine":240,"endLine":269},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-8e4d1bff-01bb-4a8d-8809-bd3ce5a5bf74-65\nfc_e7810171-6a4b-9edb-9268-d9b7529019dd_3","startedAtMs":"1784770088353","completedAtMs":"1784770088496"},"model_call_id":"3bb1eaa0-dc1e-4666-b7a1-f546fede52a6-7-wfdd","session_id":"13d95b2c-2da1-4bb3-a463-cffe162be1c5","timestamp_ms":1784770088446}
