{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"started","call_id":"call-6a6d48bf-d1a8-44fe-b0bd-8e782ba5d528-71\nfc_2c641063-83f3-9715-8ed3-2edd6e85399d_4","tool_call":{"editToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/08-内容校验规则.md","streamContent":"## 3. 工具\n\n| ruleId | 级别 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `TOOL_UNKNOWN` | error | allowedToolIds 含未注册 id |\n| `TOOL_KIND_MISMATCH` | error | 工具不允许该 cardKind |\n| `TOOL_PLAYBACK` | error | playback_only 仍声明工具 |\n| `TOOL_DIRECT_EFFECT` | error | 试图标成通话中直接 effect |\n| `TOOL_INTRODUCE_GUARD` | warning | 引荐类工具目标无 `canIntroduce` |\n\n## 3.1 Schedule / 外呼意图\n\n落盘分工见 [01 §8.1](./01-CallCard数据模型.md)、[19 §3.4](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)。\n\n| ruleId | 级别 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `SCHEDULE_ONCE_CARD_REQUIRED` | error | `schedule_call_card` 缺 `agentId`+`packageId`+`cardId` |\n| `SCHEDULE_RECURRING_CARD_REQUIRED` | error | `schedule_recurring_call` 缺 `scheduleCardId` 且缺 `cardId`+`packageId` |\n| `SCHEDULE_RECURRING_IN_STORY` | error | StoryCard 上挂 `schedule_recurring_call`（周期外呼归 ScheduleCard 宿主） |\n| `SCHEDULE_CARD_KIND` | error | recurring 目标不在 `characters/schedule-cards/`（或非法 `__free__` fallback）；**含**故事包内 `cardKind=schedule` 剧情节点冒充日常卡 |\n\n## 4. 资产 / 角色"}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-6a6d48bf-d1a8-44fe-b0bd-8e782ba5d528-71\nfc_2c641063-83f3-9715-8ed3-2edd6e85399d_4","startedAtMs":"1784770106169"},"model_call_id":"3bb1eaa0-dc1e-4666-b7a1-f546fede52a6-8-iz5l","session_id":"13d95b2c-2da1-4bb3-a463-cffe162be1c5","timestamp_ms":1784770106182}
